{
  "video_id": "Upkcp_a1vpo",
  "title": "California \"Trespassing\" Laws | Penal Code 602 PC",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4340.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "-Our common sense definition of trespassing"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7000.0,
      "end_time": 9770.0,
      "text": "is when you go on somebody else&#39;s property."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9770.0,
      "end_time": 14180.0,
      "text": "But in California law and in Penal Code Section 602,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14180.0,
      "end_time": 18200.0,
      "text": "the crime of trespassing is more likely to be charged"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18200.0,
      "end_time": 22230.0,
      "text": "in a situation where you interfere with somebody&#39;s use"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22230.0,
      "end_time": 24250.0,
      "text": "and enjoyment of their property, or you"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24250.0,
      "end_time": 26370.0,
      "text": "create a nuisance on their property,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26370.0,
      "end_time": 29410.0,
      "text": "or you refuse to leave after they tell you to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29410.0,
      "end_time": 32119.0,
      "text": "-California trespassing laws are unique in that they"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32119.0,
      "end_time": 35980.0,
      "text": "can be charged either as a felony, a misdemeanor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35980.0,
      "end_time": 37489.0,
      "text": "or an infraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37490.0,
      "end_time": 39240.0,
      "text": "The prosecutor has the discretion"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39240.0,
      "end_time": 42340.0,
      "text": "which one to file based on the individual circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42340.0,
      "end_time": 42574.0,
      "text": "of your case."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46710.0,
      "end_time": 49250.0,
      "text": "-Normally, simple trespass in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49250.0,
      "end_time": 52380.0,
      "text": "can be charged as either an infraction or a misdemeanor."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52380.0,
      "end_time": 54680.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re charged with an infraction of trespass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54680.0,
      "end_time": 57150.0,
      "text": "you most likely just face a fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57150.0,
      "end_time": 59400.0,
      "text": "However, if you&#39;re charged with a misdemeanor"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59400.0,
      "end_time": 61730.0,
      "text": "trespass in California, you face up"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61730.0,
      "end_time": 66320.0,
      "text": "to six months in county jail, or up to a $1,000 fine, or both."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66320.0,
      "end_time": 67990.0,
      "text": "In California, there&#39;s another kind of trespass"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67990.0,
      "end_time": 71990.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s more serious, and this is aggravated trespass."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71990.0,
      "end_time": 74750.0,
      "text": "Now, aggravated trespass occurs when"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74750.0,
      "end_time": 77870.0,
      "text": "you make a threat to injure someone seriously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77870.0,
      "end_time": 80850.0,
      "text": "and within 30 days of making that threat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80850.0,
      "end_time": 85320.0,
      "text": "you unlawfully enter that person&#39;s home or workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85320.0,
      "end_time": 89220.0,
      "text": "with the intent to carry out that threat that you had made."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89220.0,
      "end_time": 91910.0,
      "text": "Now, aggravated trespass can be charged"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91910.0,
      "end_time": 95240.0,
      "text": "as either a misdemeanor or a felony."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95240.0,
      "end_time": 97390.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re convicted of a misdemeanor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97400.0,
      "end_time": 100100.0,
      "text": "you face up to one year in county jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100100.0,
      "end_time": 102330.0,
      "text": "and up to a $2,000 fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102330.0,
      "end_time": 104550.0,
      "text": "However, if you&#39;re charged with aggravated trespass"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104550.0,
      "end_time": 107905.0,
      "text": "as a felony, you face up to three years in state prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107905.0,
      "end_time": 109940.0,
      "text": "and a $2,000 fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109940.0,
      "end_time": 111840.0,
      "text": "Perhaps most importantly, if you&#39;re"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111840.0,
      "end_time": 114700.0,
      "text": "convicted of a misdemeanor or a felony trespass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114700.0,
      "end_time": 116870.0,
      "text": "is that you&#39;ll then have a criminal record."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116870.0,
      "end_time": 120000.0,
      "text": "And that conviction will show up on criminal background checks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120000.0,
      "end_time": 122370.0,
      "text": "and this may prevent you from obtaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122370.0,
      "end_time": 124430.0,
      "text": "future employment or other benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128520.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131390.0,
      "text": "-Trespass can be a surprisingly difficult charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131390.0,
      "end_time": 133920.0,
      "text": "for the prosecutor to prove, and in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133920.0,
      "end_time": 135940.0,
      "text": "a lot of innocent people get wrongfully"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135940.0,
      "end_time": 137770.0,
      "text": "charged with this offense."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137770.0,
      "end_time": 140220.0,
      "text": "The good news is that here at Shouse Law Group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140220.0,
      "end_time": 142220.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve had a great record of success"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142220.0,
      "end_time": 146630.0,
      "text": "over the years in defending clients accused of trespass"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146630.0,
      "end_time": 150150.0,
      "text": "and ultimately getting their charges reduced or dismissed."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150150.0,
      "end_time": 152900.0,
      "text": "-One possible defense to the charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152900.0,
      "end_time": 154140.0,
      "text": "of criminal trespass in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154140.0,
      "end_time": 156750.0,
      "text": "is establishing that you did not interfere"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156750.0,
      "end_time": 160170.0,
      "text": "with the property owner&#39;s use or enjoyment of their property."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160170.0,
      "end_time": 163369.0,
      "text": "For example, merely entering onto somebody&#39;s property"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163370.0,
      "end_time": 166510.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t enough to establish criminal trespass."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166510.0,
      "end_time": 169130.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re going for a walk and happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169130.0,
      "end_time": 172850.0,
      "text": "to take a rest on somebody&#39;s property, be it in their grass"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172850.0,
      "end_time": 176710.0,
      "text": "or on their bench, that isn&#39;t going to be criminal trespass."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176710.0,
      "end_time": 178570.0,
      "text": "In order for it to be criminal trespass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178570.0,
      "end_time": 179920.0,
      "text": "you have to do something more."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179920.0,
      "end_time": 183619.0,
      "text": "You have to be interfering with that property owner&#39;s right"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183620.0,
      "end_time": 186550.0,
      "text": "to use their property and to enjoy their property."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186550.0,
      "end_time": 189250.0,
      "text": "-Another defense to trespass in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189250.0,
      "end_time": 191650.0,
      "text": "is that you had consent to enter the property."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191650.0,
      "end_time": 195380.0,
      "text": "Now, for example, say you go to a home of one of your friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195380.0,
      "end_time": 196880.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s throwing a party."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 196880.0,
      "end_time": 200200.0,
      "text": "And once you&#39;re there, his roommate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 200200.0,
      "end_time": 202690.0,
      "text": "that wasn&#39;t aware of the party, calls the cops"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 202690.0,
      "end_time": 204960.0,
      "text": "and says that you were trespassing."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 204960.0,
      "end_time": 207520.0,
      "text": "Now, you could assert the defense of consent"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207520.0,
      "end_time": 210840.0,
      "text": "because one of the other lawfully-residing people"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 210840.0,
      "end_time": 214100.0,
      "text": "there invited you into the home, and thereby gave you consent"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 214100.0,
      "end_time": 215560.0,
      "text": "to enter the property."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 215560.0,
      "end_time": 218100.0,
      "text": "Thus, you would not be guilty of a trespass."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 218100.0,
      "end_time": 221700.0,
      "text": "-Sometimes trespass is used as a plea"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 221700.0,
      "end_time": 223320.0,
      "text": "bargain in a more serious case."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 223320.0,
      "end_time": 225540.0,
      "text": "So for example, a person might be"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 225540.0,
      "end_time": 229179.0,
      "text": "charged with domestic violence or lewd conduct"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 229180.0,
      "end_time": 230760.0,
      "text": "or prostitution."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 230760.0,
      "end_time": 232989.0,
      "text": "And the defense lawyer reaches an agreement"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 232990.0,
      "end_time": 236270.0,
      "text": "with the prosecutor that if you would dismiss that more serious"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 236270.0,
      "end_time": 239430.0,
      "text": "charge, we&#39;ll plead guilty to trespass, sometimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239430.0,
      "end_time": 242130.0,
      "text": "as a misdemeanor, sometimes even as an infraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 242130.0,
      "end_time": 246430.0,
      "text": "And the idea is that trespass is a lot less serious"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246430.0,
      "end_time": 249840.0,
      "text": "and carries a lot less stigma than the more serious offense"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249840.0,
      "end_time": 253100.0,
      "text": "that the person was originally charged with."
    }
  ]
}